branchCategory.name: 90-RB, Shock Absorber
branchCategory.description: <p>The 90-RB shock absorber has a specially designed  orifice that compensates for varying speeds and loads to consistently decelerate loads without  requiring additional adjustment.  The double  seal enclosure consists of a scraper and a rod seal, provides extra insurance against leakage. 90-MGP is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing.</p>
